\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 5 
\f1\b0 You 
\f0\b hypocrite
\f1\b0 , 
\f0\b first
\f1\b0  
\f0\b take
\f1\b0  the log out of your own eye, and 
\f0\b then
\f1\b0  you will see clearly to take the speck out of your brother\'92s eye. Matthew 7\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Hypocrisy isn\'92t about whether a person judges or not, but who they judge first and hardest.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We live in a day where we\'92re told not to judge others actions because no one\'92s perfect and you\'92ll be a hypocrite if you do\'85\uc0\u8232 \
\ls9\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 that\'92s not what makes a person a hypocrite\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
